One Winner Will Receive:​
• One (1) Tovolo All-in-One Citrus Juicer and Zester ​
• One (1) Tovolo Citrus Slicer and Wedger​
• Two (2) 2 lb bags of Wonderful Seedless Lemons​
• One (1) 5 lb bag of Wonderful Halos ​

Giveaway Rules:​
1. Open to legal residents of the 50 United States and D.C, and must be 18+ to enter.​
2. Giveaway closes on Thursday, July 2, 2025 at 11:59 PM PDT.​
3. This giveaway is in no way affiliated with Instagram and there is no purchase necessary to enter.​

https://bit.ly/4ljQKDS​
5. Two winners will be chosen at random and contacted via direct message from @wonderfulseedlesslemons​
